{"tid":1810381,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【明報集團】2019年風雲人物：「香港警察」","createTime":"2020-01-03T22:52:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T08:32:23.000Z","uid":202464,"like":2,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca028d9a3be9538e373c08143aff6613333133a","tid":1810381,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T22:52:48.000Z","msg":"總部位於香港的《亞洲週刊》（英語：Yazhou Zhoukan；英文縮寫為YZZK）最新一期，評選「香港警察」為「2019年度風雲人物」：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeAmEdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXeAmEdh.jpg&h=18a48fdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「在關鍵的時刻，他們（港警）影響了歷史的進程，守衞香港的法治。他們是香港社會的『定海神針』，是香港市民福祉的『守護天使』。」<br />\n<br />\n文中提到，有香港人打算提名港警競逐「諾貝爾和平獎」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《亞洲週刊》係明報集團的一員。<br />\n「明報集團」加上馬來西亞「星洲媒體」及「南洋報業」，合併成為「世界華文媒體」"},{"pid":"0b7a20a1a9f66216da3a7966597dbb74df61f5a9","tid":1810381,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T23:08:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ec1d1955f2e3bb7d0fddcb069660651def80b9","tid":1810381,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T23:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a2f7914bab31196db88a7246f1ecaf345700c18","tid":1810381,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T23:18:33.000Z","msg":"正想出個post講下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知俾思兄你開咗先"},{"pid":"c548cd5d4d23e847dcd3edf903fc6565cf7d48b6","tid":1810381,"uid":96565,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"5ca028d9a3be9538e373c08143aff6613333133a","tid":1810381,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T22:52:48.000Z","msg":"總部位於香港的《亞洲週刊》（英語：Yazhou Zhoukan；英文縮寫為YZZK）最新一期，評選「香港警察」為「2019年度風雲人物」：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XeAmEdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3